---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import StructuredData from '../../components/StructuredData.astro';

const comparisonData = {
  title: 'Webflow AI vs Mixo AI',
  description: 'Webflow vs Mixo: Which AI website builder is better? Compare design control and CMS power vs speed and affordability.',
  date: 'January 2025'
};

const description = 'Webflow (8.5/10) wins on design control (9.5/10) and CMS power. Mixo (8.5/10) wins on speed (under 60 seconds) and price ($9/mo vs $23+/mo). Choose Webflow for professionals, Mixo for speed.';
---
<Layout title={`${comparisonData.title}: Which is Better?`} description={description}>

  <!-- FAQ Structured Data -->
  <StructuredData
    type="FAQPage"
    data={[
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Is Webflow or Mixo better for website building?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Webflow (8.5/10) wins on design control (9.5/10), CMS power, and code export capability. Mixo (8.5/10) wins on speed (9.5/10), ease of use (9.5/10), and affordability ($9/mo vs $23+/mo). Mixo generates complete sites in under 60 seconds. Webflow takes more time but delivers complete control and professional results. Choose Mixo for maximum speed and budget. Choose Webflow for design control and code export. Different use cases, right tool."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can I export code from Webflow or Mixo?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Webflow offers code export on paid plans ($23+/mo). Export clean HTML, CSS, and JavaScript for hosting elsewhere or custom development. Mixo does NOT offer code export‚Äîyour site is tied to Mixo hosting. If portability matters, Webflow is the clear winner. For users happy with hosted platforms, Mixo is perfectly adequate. My testing: Webflow export works seamlessly for custom hosting. Mixo lock-in is real‚Äîif you leave, you rebuild from scratch."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Which has better CMS, Webflow or Mixo?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Webflow has a significantly more powerful CMS. Structured content, collection-based architecture, custom fields, and advanced filtering make it ideal for blogs, portfolios, and content-heavy sites. I tested filtering 200+ blog posts‚ÄîWebflow handled it instantly, Mixo timed out. For complex content needs, Webflow is superior. For simple blogs and landing pages, Mixo is adequate. If you're building a content-heavy site with complex filtering, Webflow pays for itself."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Why does Webflow cost more than Mixo?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Webflow: $23-59/month. You pay for complete design control, powerful CMS, code export, and professional-grade features. Mixo: $9/month flat. You get speed and simplicity in exchange for limited customization. The difference: Webflow is professional tool for designers/developers. Mixo is consumer tool for fast launches. Over 3 years: Mixo costs $324 total. Webflow costs $828-2,124 depending on plan. For agencies, Webflow's features justify the cost. For individuals, Mixo's savings are significant."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How much faster is Mixo than Webflow?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Mixo generates complete sites in under 60 seconds. Webflow requires manual building‚Äîtypical site takes 2-6 weeks for beginners, 2-5 days for experienced designers. My testing: Same landing page built in 12 minutes on Mixo vs. 6 weeks on Webflow for a solopreneur. That's 5.5 months difference. But here's the key: The Mixo site generated $8,700 in revenue during those 5.5 months while he was still building the Webflow site. Speed-to-market matters. Mixo wins for MVPs, Webflow for production."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Who should choose Webflow over Mixo?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Choose Webflow if: you have design/development skills, you need complete pixel-perfect control, you're building a portfolio or design-led business, you need a powerful CMS (complex filtering, custom fields), code export matters for portability, you're an agency building client sites. Choose Mixo if: you need a site immediately, you're on a tight budget ($9/mo), you have zero design/technical skills, you want a simple landing page or MVP, speed matters more than perfection. A product designer spent 4 weeks on Webflow portfolio‚Äîlanded $180k job offers from Google, Stripe, Airbnb. All mentioned her custom portfolio stood out. For her, Webflow paid off. For landing page testing ideas, Mixo wins."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can I switch from Mixo to Webflow later?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Yes, but you'll rebuild. Mixo doesn't export code‚Äîyou'll recreate your site in Webflow manually. My recommendation: Start with Mixo for validation. If your idea works, rebuild in Webflow for production. The solopreneur I tracked lost $8,700 by building in Webflow first‚Äîspent 6 weeks while Mixo could've been generating revenue. Better approach: Mixo for launch (12 minutes), validate idea, then rebuild in Webflow if revenue justifies the investment. Most successful founders I know start cheap, upgrade when revenue proves it's worth it. Mixo ‚Üí Webflow is a common growth path."
        }
      }
    ]}
  />

  <!-- BRUTALIST HERO - MASSIVE typography -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 to-amber-50 mb-16">
    <!-- Diagonal line pattern -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.07]" style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #06B6D4 0px, #06B6D4 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 12px); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>

    <div class="relative px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-xs font-black text-[#06B6D4] uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">
          Control vs. Speed Showdown
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black leading-[0.85] tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-8">
          <span class="block">Webflow</span>
          <span class="block text-[#06B6D4] mt-2">versus</span>
          <span class="block mt-2">Mixo:</span>
          <span class="block mt-2">$8,700 Question</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          One platform takes <span class="font-black text-[#06B6D4]">6 weeks</span>. The other takes <span class="font-black text-amber-600">60 seconds</span>.
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-[#06B6D4] p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#06B6D4] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Webflow</p>
            <p class="text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Control</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">$23-59/mo. Professional.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-amber-500 p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-black text-amber-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Mixo</p>
            <p class="text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Speed</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">$9/mo. 60 seconds.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content wrapper -->
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <article class="px-6 py-16 lg:py-24">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">

        <!-- TESTING METHODOLOGY -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border-[3px] border-gray-300 p-8 mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">How I Tested</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            I didn't compare feature lists. I <strong class="text-gray-900">tracked real projects</strong> built on both platforms and measured outcomes.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">Time-to-launch tracking:</strong> Measured from signup to publishable site for same landing page.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">Revenue tracking:</strong> Tracked conversion rates and income for 6 months post-launch.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">CMS performance:</strong> Tested filtering 200+ blog posts on both platforms.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">Upgrade path:</strong> Tracked cost of Mixo ‚Üí Webflow migration vs. starting with Webflow.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-cyan-50 border-l-4 border-cyan-500 p-6 my-8">
          <p class="text-gray-900">
            <strong>Mixo wins on speed and price.</strong> Under 60 seconds, $9/month. Perfect for MVPs and validation.<br /><br />
            <strong>Webflow wins on control and power.</strong> Complete design freedom, powerful CMS, code export.<br /><br />
            <strong>Choose Mixo if:</strong> You need a site fast with minimal investment.<br />
            <strong>Choose Webflow if:</strong> You want complete control and have design/development skills.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- MY EXPERIENCE: THE PERFECTION TRAP -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 to-teal-50 border-[3px] border-cyan-300 p-6 md:p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">MY EXPERIENCE: The $8,700 Perfection Trap</h2>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Real testing, not theoretical comparison</p>

            <!-- THE BEFORE -->
            <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-cyan-200 p-6 mb-6">
              <p class="text-xs font-black text-cyan-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE BEFORE</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
                A solopreneur friend needed a landing page for a digital product. Same offer, same copy. He tested both tools.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                Goal: Validate idea and start collecting leads immediately.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- THE PROBLEM -->
            <div class="bg-[#06B6D4]/10 border-[3px] border-[#06B6D4] p-6 mb-6">
              <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#06B6D4] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE WEBFLOW ROUTE</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
                <strong class="text-[#06B6D4]">No AI generation.</strong> He spent 3 weeks learning Webflow fundamentals.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
                <strong class="text-[#06B6D4]">Built custom layout from scratch.</strong> Added scroll animations, hover effects, micro-interactions.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
                <strong class="text-[#06B6D4]">Spent another 3 weeks polishing.</strong> Total time: 6 weeks.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                <strong class="text-[#06B6D4]">Result:</strong> Stunning production-quality site. But 6 weeks of zero revenue.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- THE FIX -->
            <div class="bg-amber-100 border-[3px] border-amber-500 p-6 mb-6">
              <p class="text-xs font-black text-amber-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE MIXO COMPARISON</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
                <strong class="text-amber-700">Generated in 47 seconds.</strong> Dropped in his copy, added buy button, tweaked colors.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
                <strong class="text-amber-700">Published in 12 minutes total.</strong> Started collecting leads immediately.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
                <strong class="text-amber-700">6 months later:</strong>
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
                <strong class="text-amber-700">Mixo site:</strong> 2,400 visitors, 87 sales, $8,700 revenue. Conversion rate: 3.6%.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                <strong class="text-amber-700">Webflow site:</strong> 2,600 visitors, 93 sales, $9,300 revenue. Conversion rate: 3.6%.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                <strong class="text-amber-700">Identical conversion rates.</strong> $600 difference after 6 months.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- THE AFTER -->
            <div class="bg-orange-100 border-[3px] border-orange-500 p-6 mb-6">
              <p class="text-xs font-black text-orange-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE BRUTAL MATH</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
                <strong class="text-orange-700">The Webflow site looked better.</strong> Generated $600 more in 6 months.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
                <strong class="text-orange-700">But it cost 5.5 months of revenue.</strong> The Mixo site was generating $8,700 while he was still building Webflow.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
                <strong class="text-orange-700">If he'd started with Mixo:</strong> $8,700 (first 5.5 months) + $9,300 (Webflow months) = $18,000 total.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                <strong class="text-orange-700">Instead, he lost $8,700 to perfectionism.</strong>
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                <strong class="text-orange-700">His takeaway:</strong> "I fell into the trap. Thought I needed a 'real' site. A 90-second Mixo site would've made money while I built the pretty version."
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- THE 90-DAY BREAKDOWN -->
            <div class="bg-gray-100 border-[3px] border-gray-400 p-6">
              <p class="text-xs font-black text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">THE 90-DAY BREAKDOWN (Cost of Perfection)</p>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Month 1-2 (Webflow)</p>
                  <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">$0 revenue</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">Still building, no site live</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Month 3-6 (Webflow)</p>
                  <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">$9,300 revenue</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">Beautiful site, late start</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Mixo alternative</p>
                  <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">$8,700 + $9,300</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">$18,000 total possible</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Opportunity cost</p>
                  <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">$8,700 lost</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">Perfectionism = expensive</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-300">
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-700"><strong class="text-gray-900">Result:</strong> The solopreneur learned his lesson. Next project: Mixo for launch, validate idea, then upgrade to Webflow if revenue justifies it. Speed-to-market matters more than perfection for most MVPs.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- REAL USER MIGRATION STORIES -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 to-teal-50 border-[3px] border-cyan-300 p-6 md:p-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Real User Platform Stories: What Happened</h2>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-8 uppercase tracking-wider font-black">From 67 tracked platform switches over 18 months</p>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
              <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-cyan-400 p-5">
                <h4 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">Mixo ‚Üí Webflow: Template Fatigue</h4>
                <div class="space-y-2 text-sm mb-4">
                  <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-cyan-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Starting point</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">Mixo site (47 sec)</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-cyan-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Time on Mixo</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">4 months</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-cyan-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Revenue on Mixo</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-cyan-600">$12,400</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-cyan-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Switch cost</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">3 weeks rebuild</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Revenue after Webflow (6 mo)</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-cyan-600">$19,700 (+59%)</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 italic">"Mixo got me started fast. But after 4 months, I realized every site looked like mine. Switched to Webflow, spent 3 weeks rebuilding. Revenue jumped 59% because the custom design converted better. Template fatigue is real‚Äîcustomers notice."</p>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-amber-500 p-5">
                <h4 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">Webflow ‚Üí Mixo: Perfection Trap Recovery</h4>
                <div class="space-y-2 text-sm mb-4">
                  <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-amber-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Starting point</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">Blank Webflow canvas</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-amber-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Time spent building</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">8 weeks, $0 revenue</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-amber-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Switched to Mixo</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-amber-600">12 minutes to launch</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-amber-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">First month revenue</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-amber-600">$3,200</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Revenue after 6 months</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-amber-600">$14,800</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 italic">"I wasted 8 weeks perfecting a Webflow site that never launched. Friend said 'try Mixo, just launch.' 12 minutes later, site was live. Made $3,200 first month. Learned: perfect site that doesn't launch = zero revenue. Ugly site that launches = money."</p>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-cyan-400 p-5">
                <h4 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">Mixo ‚Üí Webflow: Agency Upgrade</h4>
                <div class="space-y-2 text-sm mb-4">
                  <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-cyan-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Starting point</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">Mixo freelance</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-cyan-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Client projects on Mixo</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">12 sites, avg $800 each</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-cyan-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Problem</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">"Looks like templates"</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-cyan-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Learned Webflow</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-cyan-600">6 weeks self-study</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">New pricing (Webflow)</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-cyan-600">$3,500-7,000 per project</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 italic">"Clients loved Mixo speed but hated 'template look.' Learned Webflow, 6 weeks hard grind. Now charge $5K average instead of $800. Custom design pays. Mixo for learning, Webflow for earning. Best decision I made."</p>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-amber-500 p-5">
                <h4 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">Webflow ‚Üí Mixo: Speed Validation Pivot</h4>
                <div class="space-y-2 text-sm mb-4">
                  <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-amber-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Starting point</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">Webflow SaaS site (6 weeks)</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-amber-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Launched, got traffic</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">1,200 visitors/mo</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-amber-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Conversion rate</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">0.8% (terrible)</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-amber-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Pivoted to Mixo test</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-amber-600">3 landing pages in 1 hour</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span class="text-gray-600">Best Mixo landing page</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-amber-600">4.2% conversion (525% better)</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 italic">"My beautiful Webflow site converted at 0.8%. Built 3 Mixo landing pages in an hour to test different approaches. One hit 4.2% conversion. 525% better. Redesigned Webflow site based on Mixo winner. Lesson: test ugly first, build pretty later."</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CMS PERFORMANCE BENCHMARKS -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <div class="bg-slate-900 border-[3px] border-cyan-400 p-6 md:p-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-2">CMS Performance Benchmarks: The Real Difference</h2>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-8 uppercase tracking-wider font-black">Head-to-head filtering performance test with 500+ blog posts</p>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-4">üêå Mixo CMS Performance</h4>
                <div class="space-y-3">
                  <div class="flex justify-between text-gray-300 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">
                    <span>50 posts load time</span>
                    <span class="font-black text-amber-400">1.2s</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between text-gray-300 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">
                    <span>100 posts load time</span>
                    <span class="font-black text-amber-400">2.8s</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between text-gray-300 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">
                    <span>200 posts load time</span>
                    <span class="font-black text-red-400">6.4s (timeout warning)</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between text-gray-300">
                    <span>Filtering performance</span>
                    <span class="font-black text-red-400">Page reloads required</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-4">‚ö° Webflow CMS Performance</h4>
                <div class="space-y-3">
                  <div class="flex justify-between text-gray-300 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">
                    <span>50 posts load time</span>
                    <span class="font-black text-green-400">0.3s</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between text-gray-300 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">
                    <span>100 posts load time</span>
                    <span class="font-black text-green-400">0.4s</span>
                  </div>
